    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age. The engine starts and runs consistently, but there are some minor oil seeps and the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and is prepared for some upcoming routine maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior shows well with a consistent shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches typical of regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; the upholstery is in great shape with no tears, although there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, runs smoothly, and all major features are fully functional. It represents a solid, reliable choice for someone looking for a quality vehicle that has been cared for without the premium price of a showroom-perfect model.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this stunning vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that has been meticulously cared for. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier car that offers peak performance and looks brand new in every way!",
      "price": 48500.0,
