    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved specimen, which stands as a testament to uncompromising automotive care. This vehicle remains in exemplary condition, mirroring its original showroom presentation in both aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Every surface has been maintained to an exacting standard, offering a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality. This is an investment-grade offering for those who demand the absolute peak of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
