      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an impeccable standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This example exhibits a showroom-quality finish, characterized by flawless bodywork and an interior that remains in pristine, original condition. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and vigor of its first day in service. For the discerning driver who demands nothing short of excellence, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity to acquire a distinguished asset of unrivaled integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
